Create rank based Mahalanobis distance matrix

get_mahalanobis_mat.Rd

Create rank based Mahalanobis distance matrix

Usage

get_mahalanobis_mat(X)

Arguments

X

Matrix or dataframe to calculate distances with

Value

Rank based Mahalanobis distance matrix
